 5 p.m. PST</p><p style="line-height: 1.5\;"><strong>Instructor:</strong> 
 James Gurule\, MA\, LPC</p><p style="line-height: 1.5\;"><strong>Cost:</s
 trong> $525\, includes 30 CEUs. Lewis &amp\; Clark Alumni save 20%</p><p 
