ATTACH:https://www.lclark.edu/live/image/gid/259/width/80/height/80/crop/
 1/src_region/0,0,858,980/112583_Rich_Peck_2.rev.1774466031.png
X-LIVEWHALE-TYPE:events
X-LIVEWHALE-ID:388219
X-LIVEWHALE-TIMEZONE:America/Los_Angeles
X-LIVEWHALE-IMAGE:https://www.lclark.edu/live/image/gid/259/width/80/heig
 ht/80/crop/1/src_region/0\,0\,858\,980/112583_Rich_Peck_2.rev.1774466031.
 png
X-LIVEWHALE-IMAGE-CAPTION:Richard "Rich" Peck
X-LIVEWHALE-CONTACT-INFO:<p>\n  The Dean's Office<br />\n  casdean@lclark
 .edu\n</p>
X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  Rich Peck\, a cornerstone of the Lewis &amp\; 
 Clark community for over three decades\, passed away peacefully on Sunday
 \, March 22. All are invited to honor Rich's life and his enduring legacy
  at Lewis &amp\; Clark at a Celebration of Life on Sunday\, March 29\, at
  10:00 a.m. in the Flanagan Chapel\, with a reception to follow at the Gr
 egg Pavilion.\n</p>
END:VEVENT
