SUMMARY:Tax Webinar for Immigrant & Non-Immigrant Communities
DESCRIPTION:The purpose of this informational webinar is to provide essen
 tial knowledge about tax policies and terminology. Our presenters will pr
 ovide information on the tax implications of employment onboarding\, how 
 to comply with tax filing obligations without an SSN\, and related topics
 . This webinar is for educational learning purposes\; no specific tax adv
 ice will be given.  This presentation is targeted towards international\,
  undocumented\, mixed-status families and students. Attendees with or wit
 hout Social Security Numbers are encouraged to attend\, including those w
 ith TPS\, SIJS\, and DACA. Families are welcome. The audience will not be
  visible to anyone but the presenters.Webinar details:  Thursday\, April 
 2nd  6:00 - 7:30 pmtinyurl.com/IMETaxWebinar (tinyurl.com/IMETaxWebinar)
