 ent" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read more</a> of our emotional conten
 t statement</p><hr /><h2><strong>Details &amp\; Registration</strong></h2
 ><p style="line-height: 1.5\;"><strong>Date and Time:</strong> Saturdays\
 , April 4 &amp\; 11\, 2026\, 11 a.m.-3:30 p.m. PT\, Online</p><p style="l
 ine-height: 1.5\;"><strong>Instructor:</strong> Renee Fitzpatrick\, LMHC\
 , LPC\, CST</p><p style="line-height: 1.5\;"><strong>Cost and Credits:</s
 trong> $160\, includes 8 CEUs. Alumni\, Adjuncts\, and GSEC Clinical Supe
