 ex Therapist currently working with individuals\, families and relationsh
 ip-systems with her private practice with OR and WA-based clients. Renee 
 is also an adjunct professor for the CMHC\, CTSP and MCFT programs within
  Lewis &amp\; Clark's Graduate School for Counseling Education. Renee spe
 cializes in working with sexually-marginalized communities\, including di
 sabled and neurodivergent clients. Renee is a clinician with lived experi
 ence having OCD who provides Exposure &amp\; Response Prevention Treatmen
