 en will discuss the requirements for the Environmental &amp\; Natural Res
 ources Certificate and the Energy\, Innovation\, and Sustainability Law c
 ertificate.  They will also cover available environmental courses\, pract
 ical skills experiences\, and other opportunities at Lewis &amp\; Clark. 
 Great session for 1L's thinking about their trajectory in law school and 
 for 2L's approaching their final year and applying for either certificate
 .
