 </a></strong> (she/they)\, is an IFS trained therapist in WA with special
 izations in sex therapy and psychedelic assisted therapy (PAT). Their pra
 ctice prioritizes folx who identify as BIPOC\, LGBTQIA+\, and/or neurodiv
