X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  Love working with people? This one's for you. 
 Led by adjunct professors Collin McKean and Troy Nixon\, Client Counselin
 g Moot Court builds real interviewing and counseling skills through hands
 -on practice. The semester culminates in an intra-school competition\, wi
 th top teams advancing to the American Bar Association regional competiti
 on. Enrollment is limited ŌĆö don't wait to register! RSVP <a href="https
 ://forms.gle/vwjCapjsgv2JYhHS6">here</a>.\n</p>
END:VEVENT
