 illows\, yoga mats\, blankets\, etc. for participation. We also recommend
  wearing comfortable clothing for a variety of movement\, including sitti
 ng on the floor or in a chair.</p><hr /><h2><strong>Details &amp\; Regist
 ration</strong></h2><p style="line-height: 1.5\;"><strong>Date and Time:<
 /strong> Friday\, April 10\, 2026\, 9 a.m.-4 p.m. &#160\;</p><p style="li
 ne-height: 1.5\;"><strong>Instructor:</strong> Rosario Sammartino\, PhD\,
  RSME\, RSMT</p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Lewis &amp\; Clark Graduate
  School\, Portland\, Oregon</p><p style="line-height: 1.5\;"><strong>Cost
