  is a Registered Dietitian in Oregon and Washington. She works at Nutriti
 on Studio in Portland and specializes in working with adults and adolesce
 nts with eating disorders\, disordered eating\, and individuals looking t
 o improve their relationship with food and body who also need nutrition s
 upport for medical conditions. Mikalah is a member of the Columbia River 
