 eys\, LPC</strong> has been practicing integrative somatic psychotherapy 
 since 2006. She is dedicated to offering trauma-informed\, holistic thera
 py that addresses systemic\, environmental and relational impacts through
  one's lifespan. Julianna offers equitable\, existential and somatic orie
 nted supervision clinical supervision as an approved supervisor for the O
