 ;">Identify and explain personal hope practice  </li><li style="line-heig
 ht: 1.5\;">Understand one to three leverage points for enacting change ca
 n be utilized to support transgender communities in the current political
  climate  </li></ul><p style="line-height: 1.5\;">  This training is for 
 anyone supporting trans and gender-diverse youthŌĆöincluding educators\, 
 therapists\, health care providers\, organizers\, parents\, and caregiver
 sŌĆöand is designed to deepen understanding of our current moment while e
 mbedding liberatory\, trans-centered practices into daily life and work.<
 /p><p style="line-height: 1.5\;">  This workshop may meet the OBLPCT Cult
 ural Competence Continuing Education requirement. <a href="http://www.ore
