X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p style="line-height: 1.5\;">  Research is 
 clear that early vocabulary experiences directly correlate to later acade
 mic achievements\, yet many of our students lack sufficient vocabulary to
  successfully access grade level content.&#160\;</p><p style="line-height
 : 1.5\;">  Through this hands-on workshop\, K-8 teachers\, paraeducators\
 , and school leaders will identify high-leverage vocabulary strategies an
 d learn ways to implement manageable shifts that foster deep\, lasting st
